907
01:15:06,006 --> 01:15:07,508
-Tu dzirdi?
-Laid vaļā.

908
01:15:07,591 --> 01:15:09,844
-Paklausies.
-Laid mani vaļā.

909
01:15:09,969 --> 01:15:11,637
Labi, labi, piedod.

910
01:15:11,720 --> 01:15:14,348
Bet vari mirklīti uzgaidīt?

911
