Tev ir taisnība.

920
01:15:50,009 --> 01:15:54,221
Nu, vairs nav, par ko strīdēties.

921
01:15:55,222 --> 01:15:56,599
Ja vien vari šo salabot.

922
01:15:58,684 --> 01:16:01,812
Tu, stulbais kuces d...

923
01:16:09,779 --> 01:16:11,572
